{"tid":1067103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中四男生運動場上體育課 跑步後暈倒送院不治","createTime":"2019-03-18T10:02:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T17:48:58.000Z","uid":77189,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a5572ce51551aae0ea9cf3ca4a2a9afa2bfb2e42","tid":1067103,"uid":77189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T10:02:06.000Z","msg":"上午10時22分，荃灣城門道21號城門谷運動場，警方接報一名19歲姓肖男生，在運動場跑步後暈倒，由救護車送往仁濟醫院後證實不治。警方正展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n男生在附近路德會呂明才中學讀中四，該校校長馬玉娟稱，今早體育堂，老師帶領兩班男同學20多人，到400米外的城門谷運動場上課。當時只開始一會，其間有學生跑步，但不算劇烈，稍後該名男生在場邊踱步時暈倒。體育老師連忙替他急救，並通知學校報警，惜男生送院搶救後不治。<br />\n校長續稱，男生成績中等，品行良好，喜歡運動，如跑步和球類，未聞他近日患病，同學也表示事主今日返學時，並無異樣。<br />\n<br />\n校方稍後發家長信通知其他家長及學生，並會留意同學的情緒，提供支援及輔導。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190318/59381460\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190318%2F59381460&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKiL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=24612867\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190318%2F59381460&h=0bbdcf35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190318/59381460</a>"},{"pid":"4f74048c8b328136264cbae9a723e683daeb3892","tid":1067103,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T10:02:51.000Z","msg":"近排好似多左學生猝死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知係咪讀書太辛苦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fe30a3a8adda50cd9888b8d47b07a355bdbb0c8","tid":1067103,"uid":57549,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T10:02:56.000Z","msg":"大陸新移民 -1"},{"pid":"4756c22f1a589c12c1901197185bbe749de9438a","tid":1067103,"uid":198244,"like":20,"dislike":